properties.name: discord.token
properties.description: Discord token used for the gateway authentication.

properties.name: discord.guild-id
properties.description: ID of the guild that is managed by the bot.

properties.name: discord.art-channel-id
properties.description: Id of the channel from which the images are pulled by the owner.

properties.name: discord.repost-channel-id
properties.description: Id of the channel to which the images are reposted periodically.

properties.name: discord.repost-interval
properties.description: Number of seconds between reposting images.

properties.name: discord.developer-id
properties.description: Id of the bot developer so that the bot can ping me if shit gets wrong.
